            Bio
            I am a first year Psychiatry MSc student at University of
            São Paulo, Brazil. My research is centered around cognitive
            facets of insomnia. For my thesis project I am applying
            psychometric models to validate and investigate
            sleep-related cognition scales with a Brazilian sample.
            I have plans to apply to PhD programs in Quantitative
            Psychology or related areas for Fall 2023. If you believe I
            could be a good fit for your lab or anyone’s you know,
            please feel free to reach out. Contact for collaboration on
            research or just chatting are also very welcome (preferably
            via twitter or email). You can acess my CV here
            
            
            
